===========================
  check_po_file.py - NEWS
===========================

This file contains a list of changes for each released version of
check_po_file.py.


0.8.0 (2010-12-05)
==================

New features:

- Recognize and handle byte order mark (BOM)
- Base script exit code on errors occurred/findings
- Add option to show a summary (-s/--summary)

Bugfixes:

- Process files in sorted order (by path); try to ignore duplicate paths
- Small output improvements


0.7.1 (2010-08-16)
==================

New features:

- Initial release
